\label{eq:mess_eq}
\end{equation}
where  $\sigma_n^2$ is the variance of the observation noise, ${\bf x}_k$ is the regression vector and ${\bf w}_k$ is the parameter vector to be sequentially estimated, both $M$-dimensional column vectors.


